create a file with ".robot" extension.
Indentation is mandatory.
Tab should be used for non continuation words. (Assigning value, 2 or more than 2 Tab)
Note: Download the EdgeDriver & put it in the Project

4 sections should inside a file.
section 1 - Settings
Import Purpose
"Library     SeleniumLibrary"

section2 - Variables (optional)

section3 - Test Cases
"Testcase name"
    open browser     "url"    "browser name"
    maximize browser window
For Headless Mode Testing,
"Testcase name"
    open browser     "url"    "browser name"    options=headless=True
    maximize browser window


section4 - Keywords (optional)

Concepts:
sendkeys
explicit wait
click
Title
Print
Page source
currentlink
MultiTab Link
sleep
horizontallocation(height)
verticallocation(width)


